The Management of Ibadan Electricity Distribution Company (IBEDC) commiserates with the families of Mr Kango and Mrs Kemi Adegoke ,who died as a result of an electrical accident that happened along Iwo/Adogba road ,Oyo State.   Mrs Angela Olanrewaju, Head Branding & Corporate Communication, Business Transformation & Strategy of IBEDC IBEDC disclosed in a statement in Lagos on Saturday.    According to Olanrewaju, “We are currently working with families of the deceased at this difficult period to help provide some measure of succour.   She said that investigations have begun to ascertain the facts of the case, whilst all necessary protocols and reports to the regulatory authorities have been initiated.   “Our teams of Engineers are already carrying out safety routine maintenance to forestall such occurrences. 